DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260329T000000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260330T000000
SUMMARY:Backend B.10 Unblocked (~30 days pipeline data)
DESCRIPTION:Backtest harness (scripts/backtest.py) becomes viable around late March\nwhen >=30 days of pipeline data are available.\n\nSee: docs/research/trend-insights.md Phase B\nSee: docs/project-plan.md Backend Track B.10
