DESCRIPTION:Two topics:\n\n1. Implement the same bounced/spring physics for the remaining panels (not yet done).\n   Reference existing implementation for the panels that already have it.\n\n2. Talk through URLs to graphics — how graph data URLs are structured\,\n   what paths are used for static assets\, and any open questions about\n   image/graphic URL handling in the web client.
