UID:tour-sample-data-20260325@predictor-ingest
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260325T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260325T160000
SUMMARY:Plan self-guided new-user tour + bespoke tour dataset
DESCRIPTION:Backlog item: build a self-guided tour for new users.\n\nApproach: use the same technique we used to create the initial sample data\nset at project start — but craft a dataset specifically tuned to showcase\nevery stop on the tour brilliantly.\n\nTopics to cover:\n  1. Identify the tour stops (what graph features / interactions to highlight)\n  2. Design the tour dataset so each stop has an ideal example visible\n  3. Decide delivery mechanism (overlay tooltips\, step sequencer\, highlight pulses)\n  4. Reuse existing sample-data generation tooling\n  5. Add backlog card to docs/backlog.md and docs/project-plan.md
CATEGORIES:UI,Backlog,Task
STATUS:NEEDS-ACTION
PRIORITY:4
BEGIN:VALARM
TRIGGER:-PT10M
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:New-user tour + tour dataset planning session in 10 minutes
